{"id":905153713,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"3 weeks, 4 days","timestamp":1677392729,"status":14,"status_display":"Time Limit Exceeded","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/905153713/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Edit Distance","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\n    private String word1, word2;\n    private int n1, n2;\n    public int minDistance(String word1, String word2) {\n        this.word1 = word1;\n        this.word2 = word2;\n        n1 = word1.length();\n        n2 = word2.length();\n\n        return getAns(0,0);\n    }\n\n    private int getAns(int i, int j){\n        if(i>=n1){//insert\n            return n2-j;\n        }\n        if(j>=n2){//delete\n            return n1-i;\n        }\n        if(word1.charAt(i)==word2.charAt(j)){\n            return getAns(i+1,j+1);\n        }\n        else{\n            int ans = Math.min(getAns(i,j+1),getAns(i+1,j));\n            return 1 + Math.min(ans,getAns(i+1,j+1));\n        }\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"edit-distance","has_notes":false}
